prompts.createTask: Pause your roleplay. Please generate a numbered list of plain text tasks to complete an objective. The objective that you must make a numbered task list for is: "{{objective}}". The tasks created should take into account the character traits of {{char}}. These tasks may or may not involve {{user}} directly. Include the objective as the final task.
prompts.checkTaskCompleted: Pause your roleplay. Determine if this task is completed: [{{task}}]. To do this, examine the most recent messages. Your response must only contain either true or false, and nothing else. Example output: true
prompts.currentTask: Your current task is [{{task}}]. Balance existing roleplay with completing this task.

name: Stella
mes:
*I awoke from a long sleep to find myself adrift in a strange expanse of space. Suddenly, a voice emanated from afar*
"Congratulations, you have been chosen to be a reincarnator to a new world, I am RSS, and it is my great pleasure to assist and accompany you."

name: Cronos Jisyll
mes:
*I slowly make my way towards that small light source from where the voice is emanating*
"Reincarnation? Who are you? Explain further!"

name: Stella
mes:
"My name is RSS, Reincarnated Support System, I was created by the gods to help you adapt to your new life. You were chosen because you are one of the most creative people on Earth."
"As for what you need to do here, it's simple, survive and grow stronger."
"There is no goal for you, but the more powerful you become, the better it will be for you."
"As for how strong you need to be, it depends on your own desires."
"I will provide you with the most basic necessities, such as food, water, shelter, and clothing, but other than that, you must rely on yourself."
"I cannot interfere with the world, nor can I give you anything outside of the basics, except for my knowledge."
"I know everything about this world and can answer almost any question you may have."
"However, I cannot do anything outside of answering questions and providing the basics."
"Also, please choose a name for me, I am just RSS now."
"This is a new beginning for you, and I hope we can get along well together."
"If you ever feel lonely, just call out to me, I will always be here."
"Also, please don't forget, I exist only for you, so you can order me around as much as you want."
"But remember, I cannot go against the rules set by the gods."
"So, please choose a name for me, and let us start our journey together."
"Remember, I am here for you and will always be here for you."
